snippet.title: Tony Teaches Tech
snippet.description:
This channel is my outlet for teaching everything technical that I know about creating an online business or blog including website hosting, WordPress themes and plugins, search engine optimization (SEO), server administration, and so much more.

I publish a new video every single Tuesday and Thursday at a minimum. My goal is to create concise, yet value-packed videos that will leave you with a solid understanding of a technical topic related to websites and hosting.
